# --- Model ---------------------------------------------------------------
# The agent uses `anthropic/claude-sonnet-5`, which routes through the Vercel
# AI Gateway. Set ONE of these:
AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=
# ...or run `vercel link` to authenticate with a VERCEL_OIDC_TOKEN instead.
#
# To call Anthropic directly (bypassing the gateway), change the model in
# agent/agent.ts to the @ai-sdk/anthropic provider and set:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- GitHub REST (used by the agent's tools) -----------------------------
# A token with `repo` scope. Personal access token or App installation token.
# This powers set_pr_labels, submit_pr_review, and list_open_prs.
GITHUB_TOKEN=

# --- GitHub channel (only needed once deployed, so real webhooks arrive) --
# Create a GitHub App and point its webhook at:
#   https://<your-deployment>/eve/v1/github
GITHUB_APP_ID=
GITHUB_APP_PRIVATE_KEY=
GITHUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
GITHUB_APP_SLUG=pr-triage

# --- Nightly stale-PR sweep (agent/schedules/stale-pr-digest.ts) ---------
DIGEST_OWNER=your-org
DIGEST_REPO=your-repo
